description: Redevelopment (following demolition of the existing bus depot) to provide a part three and five storey mixed use building (incorporating part lower and upper ground floor levels) comprising 1022sqm of retail/food and drink space (A1/A2/A3 and B1a use class) and 85 self-contained flats to upper floor levels (part upper ground to fourth floor levels); vehicle/pedestrian access from Gunnersbury Lane; integral cycle parking; refuse storage and roof-top gardens, hard and soft landscaping (Re-submission following refusal of planning application ref: P/2008/3463 dated 31/12/2008)
